Package: linux-headers-bcm2709
Architecture: armhf
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-generic-bcm2709 
Description: Linux kernel headers for the BCM2709 architecture.
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for ARM BCM2709 systems.

Package: linux-image-bcm2709
Architecture: armhf
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-generic-bcm2709, linux-firmware
Description: Linux kernel image for the BCM2709 architecture.
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for ARM BCM2709 systems.

Package: linux-bcm2709
Architecture: armhf
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-bcm2709 (= ${binary:Version}), linux-headers-bcm2709 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel for the BCM2709 architecture.
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel available
 for ARM BCM2709 systems.

Package: linux-tools-bcm2709
Architecture: armhf
Section: metapackages
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-tools-${kernel-abi-version}-generic-bcm2709
Description: Linux kernel versioned Tools.
 This package will always depend on the latest Linux kernel versioned tools
 available for ARM BCM2709 systems. The Ubuntu patches have been applied.
